  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <p><img src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=98993285&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2Foylw20gGnRg4ueQ5CFiaxvnM4BIK0olvDkJGibctQHicRCbJTsFbQoL8JQBjfkiaJ5zOpVJRC5DSFBHzXULGSpvibJQ%2F0%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\">我们正生活在一个「被推送」的时代，每一条信息、每一则通知，都在以「即时性」为名试图争夺你的注意力。而 Quote/0 摘录正试图为这种规则提供另一种「自然而具体的呈现」。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\">最近推送的 1.7.0 版本固件与 1.1.3 版本 App，在系统性能提升的基础上引入多项内容服务升级，新版本带来的内容不只是等待你调用的「工具」，而是自然地融入「环境感知」以适应你的节奏。</span></span></p>\n  <h2 style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;h3&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;id&quot;:&quot;ss-hIdChildren-1&quot;,&quot;style&quot;:&quot;line-height: 1.75em; margin-bottom: 24px;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;node&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;span&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;class&quot;:&quot;s1&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 18px;color: rgb(255, 76, 65);\">▍</span></span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 18px;font-weight: bold;\">将数据融入日常</span></span></h2>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;font-weight: bold;\">新增内容</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\">：</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\">「轻牛健康」「GitHub 仓库数据」「哔哩哔哩 UP 主面板」</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\">此次更新加入「轻牛健康」内容卡片，健康数据不再隐藏在需要刻意打开的 App 中。绑定账号后，今日运动数据、卡路里摄入量等等能够以一种更自然的方式呈现在屏幕上。它不设强提醒，只是安静地存在于你的视野边缘，让你对自己的状态保持一种温和的感知。健康管理由此从一项需要意志力的任务，转变为一种自然而然的生活背景。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-imgfileid=\"100118358\" data-ratio=\"0.7482142857142857\" data-s=\"300,640\" type=\"block\" data-type=\"webp\" data-w=\"1120\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=698306de&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2Foylw20gGnRg4ueQ5CFiaxvnM4BIK0olvDGNdsm0GnEJPIfich9yDnTicq6YuHnN1nzcYx2eehalnecDAomKdfgQmQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dwebp%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\">同样的逻辑体现在「GitHub 仓库数据」与「哔哩哔哩 UP 主面板」上。对于开发者与创作者，这些数据往往关联着项目进展或个人成果，Quote/0 将其转化为一张随时可瞥见的「信息仪表盘」，焦虑地频繁刷新被替代为从容地偶尔一瞥。你与关键指标的关系，从「主动追踪」变为「被动感知」，焦点也将回归于创作本身。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-imgfileid=\"100118353\" data-ratio=\"0.7446428571428572\" data-s=\"300,640\" type=\"block\" data-type=\"webp\" data-w=\"1120\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=ad5b93a3&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2Foylw20gGnRg4ueQ5CFiaxvnM4BIK0olvDDk8U7zyP4laVHtic6RH8IQLKO4fuuj9J5a9WfVmdtpJIeL7YFA7oicicQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dwebp%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;h3&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;id&quot;:&quot;ss-hIdChildren-1&quot;,&quot;style&quot;:&quot;line-height: 1.75em; margin-bottom: 24px;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;node&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;span&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;class&quot;:&quot;s1&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 18px;color: rgb(255, 76, 65);\">▍</span></span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 18px;font-weight: bold;\">重新定义「资讯获取」</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;font-weight: bold;\">新增内容</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\">：</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\">「AI 资讯快报」「Readhub 科技资讯」「黄金走势」</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\">如何获取资讯而不被其吞没？Quote/0 给出了自己的答案：高度过滤，极简呈现。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\">「AI 资讯快报」与「Readhub 科技资讯」卡片不再是无穷滚动的信息流，它每日仅提炼最关键的几则动态，更像是一份被动送达的桌面早报，而不是一个要求你不断刷新的信息入口。在你抬头间隙，用一句话告诉你世界发生了什么。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-imgfileid=\"100118354\" data-ratio=\"0.7428571428571429\" data-s=\"300,640\" type=\"block\" data-type=\"webp\" data-w=\"1120\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=81d0bc9a&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2Foylw20gGnRg4ueQ5CFiaxvnM4BIK0olvDJlibu6vjp6PymJchJaYqNWnlUYXPInAFbhlbWwoENfIAIQx95tFQQ7g%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dwebp%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\">「黄金走势」则彻底剥离了交易工具的属性，剔除了复杂图表与实时跳动，只保留最核心的价格与趋势。它服务于那些关心资产配置但不愿盯盘的人，在「完全忽视」与「焦虑投入」之间，提供了一个优雅的平衡点——让你保持连接，却不受捆绑。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-imgfileid=\"100118357\" data-ratio=\"0.7517857142857143\" data-s=\"300,640\" type=\"block\" data-type=\"webp\" data-w=\"1120\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=e580773f&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2Foylw20gGnRg4ueQ5CFiaxvnM4BIK0olvDnszOBwdOq80NiakxSK2HBSFic8ptozV6Qp6JhA0egbxibGozImAzd61ibA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dwebp%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <h2 style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;h3&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;id&quot;:&quot;ss-hIdChildren-1&quot;,&quot;style&quot;:&quot;line-height: 1.75em; margin-bottom: 24px;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;node&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;span&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;class&quot;:&quot;s1&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 18px;color: rgb(255, 76, 65);\">▍</span></span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 18px;font-weight: bold;\">工具的「存在姿态」</span></span></h2>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;font-weight: bold;\">新增内容</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\">：</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\">「开发者平台 API」「二维码」「号码牌」「历史上的今天」「答案之书」</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\">本次更新的许多功能，重新定义了工具的存在方式：它们就在那里，却只在被需要时显现。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\">开放了「开发者平台 API」，让设备控制变得更加精细。这种「控制权」并非以复杂设置页面的形式强加于你，而是通过API静候调用。无论是列出设备、查看状态，还是切换内容，都遵循着「你需要，它响应」的节奏。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-imgfileid=\"100118355\" data-ratio=\"0.7482142857142857\" data-s=\"300,640\" type=\"block\" data-type=\"webp\" data-w=\"1120\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=51755f65&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2Foylw20gGnRg4ueQ5CFiaxvnM4BIK0olvDAyiaNhENwLNNknf7whfwRFL8LzibhEP66l6ibrlpyt67pOuLMIJNgd2eA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dwebp%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\">「二维码」「号码牌」「历史上的今天」「答案之书」……这些卡片如同桌面上摆放得当的实体工具。你不会时刻注意到它们，但在需要分享链接、记录号码、寻找一点灵感或趣味时，它们就在手边。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-imgfileid=\"100118356\" data-ratio=\"0.7491071428571429\" data-s=\"300,640\" type=\"block\" data-type=\"webp\" data-w=\"1120\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=6446c883&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2Foylw20gGnRg4ueQ5CFiaxvnM4BIK0olvD71VsO3Ix6ib0zwRTB6JSTNEHLLByzJgYtW8NDrQ1HicQscOtnUxWDh2w%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dwebp%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <h2 style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;h3&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;id&quot;:&quot;ss-hIdChildren-1&quot;,&quot;style&quot;:&quot;line-height: 1.75em; margin-bottom: 24px;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;node&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;span&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quo